name: Anica Martin
description: I am independent and energetic person. I appreciate friendship and optimistic, resilient people. But most of all I love and value my little, but strong family. I am a merry, hardworking, kind and sociable young woman. I have many friends. I like to cook and to travel very much. I live in a beautiful southern city which has interesting history and architecture. I like warmth very much and so every year I am looking forward to summer, as I am a sun babe. I like merry, sociable and open people who have a sense of humor as I am the same myself. I developed such love for sports that I cant even imagine how I was living without it. I also have a responsible attitude towards work. As for my personal life, I want to meet a soulmate, a person with whom I will be able to share my essence without being afraid to loose it. I like kind people who like animals. I admire children and treat elderly people with much respect. if you want to keeping in touch with me anicamartin909 at g mail dot com
